    "1202102": {
        "Desc": "Analyze strategy with Kokomi",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I must admit, I wasn't expecting to find the Fatui laying low in a hilichurl camp. Presumably they've been operating out of here in secret for quite some time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "What's their objective? Are the soldiers right? Could they really be in collusion with the Tenryou Commission?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Let's scour the camp for evidence. If the merchant's story is true, the inventory should be here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright! Time to take a look around."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
