    "1202108": {
        "Desc": "Report back to Kokomi",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "You know, the earliest shrine on Watatsumi Island was not located in Sangonomiya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "It was close to the Statue of The Seven. Back then, the people of this island recognized the Shogun's existence, despite not venerating her as the Shogunate do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "But after she struck down our protector deity, the shrine was abandoned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Relations between Watatsumi Island and the Shogunate have soured ever since. Mistrust has become deep-rooted over time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I've been hoping to raise all this at the peace talks and discuss it properly. Grievances have to be let go eventually..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Youkou",
                    "T": "Your Excellency, what brings you out this way on your busy schedule?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Youkou",
                    "T": "Oh my, you're looking a little worse for wear... You need to take better care of yourself, okay? All of our fates depend on you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Mm, thanks for your concern, but I'm fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuna",
                    "T": "Your Excellency, I beg you, heed a word of advice. After all this time fighting the Shogun's Army, peace is not something that can simply be declared."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuna",
                    "T": "If we reconcile with them, the god who once protected us will have died in vain..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Youkou",
                    "T": "Come on, that's ancient history. Besides, the fighting is barely over. We should be grateful to be at peace once more."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuna",
                    "T": "I know, I know, it's just... *sigh* We should remain strong in these negotiations. We mustn't be too ready to compromise."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I appreciate your concerns. I will consider the options carefully and be sure to proceed appropriately."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuna",
                    "T": "Wonderful... We're all counting on you, Your Excellency."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shiori",
                    "T": "Your Excellency? Well, I'll be! Fancy meeting you at a place like this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shiori",
                    "T": "Do you know — my daughter's enrolled herself in the shrine maiden selection process this year. If she makes it into Sangonomiya, I'll be one very happy mother! You're a kind and gracious leader. She'd be in very good hands."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shiori",
                    "T": "*sigh* I'm always telling my daughter that if she gets the chance to learn from Her Excellency directly, she must make the most of it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shiori",
                    "T": "I mean, just look at Her Excellency. Still so young, but so mature and intelligent. My daughter has always looked to you as a role model."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Well, if she comes to Sangonomiya, I'll look out for her..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iwata",
                    "T": "Ah, Your Excellency! Boy, am I glad you're here. As you know, agricultural output has taken a pretty big hit this year, let me bring you up to speed on the latest situation..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ryouko",
                    "T": "#Oh, Your Excellency, isn't this the captain of Swordfish II? Will {F#she}{M#he} be based on Watatsumi Island from now on?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yukiya",
                    "T": "Your Excellency..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Uh... Please remain calm, everyone, I'll get around to all your queries."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Though for the longer ones, I'd prefer it if you could write a report and submit it to the shrine. Then I can respond to each one as and when I have the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, are you alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Heh... This kind of thing is water off a duck's back for you, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is testing my patience."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "*sigh* Me too. It does get pretty annoying..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Izumi Naki",
                    "T": "Your Excellency, here you are."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Izumi Naki",
                    "T": "There's been a situation. We're still waiting on the delivery of a whole batch of ceremonial items. I'm beginning to worry that they've been stolen..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Oh, we retrieved those already — no need to worry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Izumi Naki",
                    "T": "Really? That's fantastic! You never cease to amaze us, Your Excellency!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Izumi Naki",
                    "T": "I sorted through all the petitions received recently and placed them on your desk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Izumi Naki",
                    "T": "Also, according to the schedule, you're just in time for your meeting today on the development of the textiles industry..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "That's today? ...Right now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Izumi Naki",
                    "T": "Yes. The two young ladies have arrived safely, we're just waiting for you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "#Mm, I see... *sigh* {NICKNAME}, I was hoping to take a walk around the island with you, but it looks like we'll have to save that for some other time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Let's rendezvous tomorrow at the entrance to Sangonomiya Shrine. Then we'll go and make preparations for the Victory Feast."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yay, the Victory Feast! Just to be clear, we're talking lots of delicious food, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Haha... That's the name of the game. There'll be some Watatsumi Island specialties which I'm sure you'll enjoy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Great! See you tomorrow then!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Mm..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
