    "1202201": {
        "Desc": "Wait till 10:00 – 12:00 the next day",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Kokomi isn't here yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's weird. She doesn't seem like the type to show up late to things... Eh, let's wait a while longer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "How is she still not here? Do you think she could be in trouble?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's go ask that soldier over there."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1202202": {
        "Desc": "Wait for Kokomi near the Sangonomiya Shrine",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Kokomi!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So this is where you ran off to! We were gonna meet up and get things ready for the Victory Feast today, what happened?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Oh... It's you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I—I apologize... I'm not feeling my usual self today."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*gasp* You got sick? We'll go find a doctor right away!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "No no, it's nothing like that... It's just, my energy is completely spent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Y—You run on energy? *gasp* You mean... you're like a Ruin Guard!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "No, it's just a figure of speech. *sigh* I'm ashamed to admit it, but I can't always be the infinitely capable person I present myself as."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Everyone was asking so much of you yesterday..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I could sense things were getting to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Oh... you noticed? I guess I haven't quite mastered the ability to hide how I'm feeling. I'll keep working at it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "To be honest, I'm not really cut out to be a leader. At first, my dream was to read up on military strategy and perhaps become an adviser."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Constantly communicating with people, trying to retain their morale, having to read between the lines, making sure everyone gets the recognition they deserve... It's such hard work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "You're somehow supposed to make people feel wonderful just from being in your presence, while also commanding their respect... It doesn't come naturally to me. Truth be told, it's something I never wanted for myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "But because of my bloodline, I was always going to end up being the Divine Priestess sooner or later. Like it or not, it's just the way it is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "So whenever I feel overwhelmed, I come here to just lose myself in a book and relax for a while..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Don't worry, it doesn't affect my work. I handed over preparations for the Victory Feast to someone else."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I have to make a speech tonight, and I mustn't give the troops any reason to suspect that something could be wrong. This peace was hard-won, and I want them to feel at ease."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is there anything we can do to help?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I should be feeling energized again soon if I hold off on work for a little longer. *sigh* If only there were some way I could listen to a good read on military strategy, I'm sure that'd speed up the process..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I was reading a book last time I was here, but I only got about halfway through. Where did I put it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We'll find it for you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And then we'll read it out to you — to help you recover!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "You'd do that for me? Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Hehe... I'm really lucky you came back to Watatsumi Island."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1202203": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Paimon",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Hey, look, {NICKNAME}. Could this be the book she wanted?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Swordfish captain came back today. Energy +4...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Ah, that's... that's just, um..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We saw nothing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(And if we did, it was all Paimon's fault.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Give. It. Here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh-heh, guess that was the wrong one... Let's keep looking."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1202205": {
        "Desc": "Go to the designated place",
        "Step": "The agreed time has come and gone, but Kokomi has yet to make her appearance. You learn of here whereabouts from the guards, but what you discover there is...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa... Look at all these petitions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So does Kokomi make time to deal with these even when she's resting?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Sangonomiya Events Cash Flow Statement,\" \"Consolidated Annual Report on Fishing Production,\" \"Watatsumi Island Monthly Maintenance Expenses Breakdown\"..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This is a lot of work for one person. And it's on top of all the directives she has to write and the people she has to meet day-to-day. It's no wonder she gets burnt out from time to time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's track down that book and help her feel like herself again!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
